     H            Y.
     F** ECSR79 *******************************************
     F*  PRINT DIE STORE LABEL DATA  REORG                *
     F*          2019.05.15  MAEDA.                       *
     F*****************************************************
     F*          FILE DEFINITION                          *
     F*****************************************************
     FECSPP78 UF  E                    DISK
     F*
     I*****************************************************
     I*          DATA STRUCTURE                           *
     I*****************************************************
     I*==< SYSTEM DATE/TIME >==*
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140S@TIME
     I                                        1   60S@HMS
     I                                        7  140S@YMD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80S@DATE
     I                                        1   40S@DAYY
     I*==< SYSTEM INFORMATION >==*
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM @@PGID
     I                                      244 253 @@WSID
     I                                      254 263 @@USID
     I                                      264 269 @@JBNO
     I            DS
     I                                        1  15 W0BAR@
     I                                        1  14 W0BA14
     C*****************************************************
     C*          MAIN ROUTINE                             *
     C*****************************************************
      *
     C                     TIME           S@TIME
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     S@DATE
     C                     SUB  2         S@DAYY
     C                     READ ECSPP78                  91
     C           *IN91     DOWEQ'0'
     C           EPKOHZ    IFLT S@DATE
     C                     DELETECSPP781
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     READ ECSPP78                  91
     C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C*
